---
title: One-Pot Plant-Based Protein & Bean Chili with Hot Sauce Crema & Monterey Jack Cheese
description: A good chili has well-seasoned protein, creamy beans, and tender vegetables. A great chili, however, has all that and comes together in one pot in under an hour. This vegetarian chili is made with plant-based protein and beans, and we’re pretty sure you’ll agree: it’s one of the greats. Not to mention, these bowls are adorned with some delicious fixings: tangy hot sauce crema and melty Monterey Jack. If you’ve got some on hand, why not crumble up some tortilla chips and sprinkle them on top for a crunch?
